<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title><%= title %></title>
	<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen bg-[#f4f6fb] text-slate-800">
  <div class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 py-10">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute -left-20 top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-rose-200/60 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-1/4 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-amber-200/40 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/3 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-indigo-200/35 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border border-white/80 bg-white/90 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-300/30 backdrop-blur">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-100 bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-50 via-white to-amber-50 px-6 py-6 sm:px-8 sm:py-7">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-rose-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-rose-700 shadow-sm">
            Server Error
          </div>

          <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">
            500 - Internal Server Error
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 sm:text-base">
            Something went wrong on the server while loading this page. It is not your fault—the app may be busy or a background step failed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="px-6 py-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-8">
          <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-500">Status</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">500</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-500">Condition</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Server Error</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-500">Suggestion</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Try Again</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
            <a
              href="/dashboard"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-slate-300/40 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-rose-700"
            >
              Go to Dashboard
            </a>

            <a
              href="javascript:location.reload()"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-slate-300"
            >
              Reload Page
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
              Try refreshing in a moment. If it keeps happening, check routes, the database, or server logs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>